description: One Year Free has come to an end and the winner has claimed the $1500 grand prize! If you didn't win then don't worry, we'll be doing this again before you know it. You can still get the app right now if you'd like to let us know if you want to be notified the next time we start giving stuff away. Thank you everyone for participating, we hope you enjoyed it as much as we did. Finally special thanks to the kind folks at webOSroundup for verifying and brokering the promotion, let's hope they are up for it again in the future. Thanks again everyone!
